What's new in Firefox Focus for Android (version 5)
This article is no longer maintained, so its content might be out of date.
Thank you for updating. Here are the changes you’ll see in this new version:
Block third-party cookies. This is off by default. To block all or third-party cookies, see
Block cookies in Firefox Focus for Android
Add custom URLs to your autocomplete list by long-tapping on the address bar. See
Autocomplete settings in the Firefox Focus address bar
